</span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/4468706a13a29ff0a1980ee6afe5d311.webp?t=1762082384\" width=761 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纽约市发生了大量人口失踪事件，引起FBI的高度重视。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FBI探员汤米·桑德森在调查一宗小女孩失踪案，不幸失足掉入后室Level 0。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/39e52f82212ad7f94ff2f5979a8192df.poster.avif?t=1762082384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/39e52f82212ad7f94ff2f5979a8192df.webm?t=1762082384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/39e52f82212ad7f94ff2f5979a8192df.mp4?t=1762082384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/1ebba5f431ed753804d4ac6ea0d346f9.webp?t=1762082384\" width=761 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏包含了Level 0~5，Level Fun等6个层级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都很大，充满挑战，每个关卡都有不同的谜题和机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/4ac386707e48ac518ca4f967ce2368ed.poster.avif?t=1762082384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/4ac386707e48ac518ca4f967ce2368ed.webm?t=1762082384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/4ac386707e48ac518ca4f967ce2368ed.mp4?t=1762082384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/047605159e10367940f4b27dfe4b4eca.webp?t=1762082384\" width=761 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含了随机生成迷宫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要每次重新进入游戏，部分区域迷宫地形将会随机变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让您每次都是不同的全新游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/87fe9a5a2aa4783a9669a2dd324f02d6.poster.avif?t=1762082384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/87fe9a5a2aa4783a9669a2dd324f02d6.webm?t=1762082384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220280/extras/87fe9a5a2aa4783a9669a2dd324f02d6.mp4?t=1762082384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
